These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-1::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, spy, family, comedy
There are 4 different favourite colors: blue, brown, blood-red, azure
City: hamburg, prague, nizza, venice
House: cottage, cape-cod, farmhouse, palace
There are 4 different nationalities: chinese, australian, mexican, italian
 1. the farmhouse house is on the left or right of the italian##3
 2. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person who likes azure##5
 3. the person who likes brown is on the far left##1
 4. the person who likes blue is the cape-cod house##1
 5. the mexican is on the right of the person who likes blue##1
 6. the cape-cod house is not to the left of the australian##8
 7. the farmhouse house is on the right of the person traveling to prague##1
 8. the farmhouse house is not to the left of the chinese##8
 9. the italian is the person watching western movies##1
10. the person watching comedy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
11. the person watching spy movies is in an even position##4
12. the mexican is on the left or right of the chinese##3
13. the person traveling to venice is not to the right of the person watching family movies##8
14. the mexican is somewhere to the left of the italian##5
15. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the farmhouse house##5
16. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the palace house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Movie-Genre    | comedy | spy     | family     | western |
| Color        | brown  | blue | blood-red      | azure      |
| City         | venice  | prague    | nizza | hamburg       |
| House       | cottage | cape-cod   | farmhouse      | palace  |
| Nationality   | australian      | chinese  | mexican   | italian      |

