 8. the fan of pop is not to the left of the person eating pear##8
 9. the fan of dubstep is not to the right of the person eating cabbage##8
10. the person eating pear is on the left or right of the fan of disco##3
11. the person who likes fuchsia is not to the left of the person who likes light-blue##8
12. the modern house is on the left of the fan of disco##1
13. the security-guard is not to the right of the fan of blues##8
14. the firefighter is not to the left of the fan of dubstep##8
15. the person who likes purple is on the right of the fan of pop##1
16. the craftsman house is on the left or right of the accountant##3
17. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the person eating papaya##3
18. the security-guard is somewhere between the victorian house and the modern house##7
