.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-13::.
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, rabbit, guinea-pig, dog
The people have 4 different jobs:  project-manager, teacher, architect, bartender
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: aconite, tulip, begonia, balloon-flower
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, lavender, green, blood-red
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, tram, train, car
 1. the teacher is somewhere to the right of the architect##5
 2. the person who likes lavender is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the bartender is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 4. the person who growstulip is not to the right of the person who growsaconite##8
 5. the owner of the dog is not to the left of the person who growsbegonia##8
 6. the person who growsbegonia is not to the right of the teacher##8
 7. the bartender is on the left of the project-manager##1
 8. the person who likes lavender is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1
10. the owner of the rabbit is not to the left of the person driving the train##8
11. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
12. the person driving the trike is on the left or right of the person who growsballoon-flower##3
13. the person who growstulip is not the person who likes apricot##6
14. the person who growstulip is not to the left of the person driving the tram##8
15. the bartender is between the owner of the guinea-pig and the person who likes green##2
16. the person who growsbegonia is somewhere to the left of the owner of the goldfish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Pet          | rabbit   | goldfish   | guinea-pig    | dog      |
| Job         | architect  | bartender | project-manager    | teacher    |
| Flower   | begonia  | tulip       | balloon-flower       | aconite  |
| Color   | green | blood-red   | apricot | lavender |
| Transport         | train   | tram     | car   | trike   |

