.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-14::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: yellow, red, emerald, fuchsia
House: cape-cod, art-deco, modern, townhouse
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, rock, reggae, blues
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, lily, begonia, rose
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, polish, nigerian, british
 1. the fan of reggae is on the right of the person who likes red##1
 2. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
 3. the polish is somewhere to the left of the british##5
 4. the cape-cod house is not to the right of the person who growsbegonia##8
 5. the townhouse house is on the right of the fan of blues##1
 6. the nigerian is not to the right of the person who growsbegonia##8
 7. the polish is somewhere to the left of the person who growsbegonia##5
 8. the person who growslily is not the person who likes red##6
 9. the person who likes yellow is not to the right of the polish##8
10. the person who growsrose is between the person who growslily and the cape-cod house##2
11. the person who likes red is somewhere to the left of the person who growsamaryllis##5
12. the person who growsrose is not to the left of the nigerian##8
13. the art-deco house is the person who likes emerald##1
14. the canadian is on the left or right of the fan of rock##3
15. the polish is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
16. the canadian is not to the right of the person who likes red##8

.:: Answer ::.
