4 different games are played: chess, whist, snooker, canasta
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, dutch, turkish, french
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, freelancer, doctor, writer
 1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the palace house##1
 2. the cape-cod house is on the right of the analyst##1
 3. the french is on the left of the pakistani##1
 4. the person playing snooker is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in december##8
 5. the writer is not to the left of the cape-cod house##8
 6. the freelancer is not the farmhouse house##6
 7. the french is somewhere to the right of the futuristic house##5
 8. the person playing snooker is not the person who's birthday is in october##6
 9. the person who's birthday is in november is somewhere to the left of the cape-cod house##5
10. the farmhouse house is in an odd position##4
11. the person playing whist is not the farmhouse house##6
12. the analyst is not to the right of the person playing snooker##8
13. the doctor is on the far left or far right##3
14. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left or right of the turkish##3
15. the farmhouse house is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
16. the palace house is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
17. the person playing canasta is somewhere to the right of the doctor##5
18. the dutch is on the far left or far right##3
19. the farmhouse house is somewhere to the right of the person playing whist##5
20. the person playing chess is not to the left of the farmhouse house##8
21. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in october##8

