 3. the person eating potato is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
 4. the baccarat-smoker is not to the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
 5. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person eating apple##1
 6. the siglo-smoker is somewhere to the right of the montecristo-smoker##5
 7. the ranch-style house is on the right of the art-deco house##1
 8. the ranch-style house is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person eating avocado is not to the left of the blend-smoker##8
10. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the siglo-smoker##1
11. the person who's birthday is in november is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
12. the baccarat-smoker is on the far right##1
