 5. the person traveling to london is not to the left of the person who's birthday is in july##8
 6. the owner of the lizard is not to the left of the turkish##8
 7. the person traveling to berlin is not the craftsman house##6
 8. the person traveling to london is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 9. the person traveling to new-york is not to the right of the person who's birthday is in august##8
10. the owner of the rat is on the far left or far right##3
11. the person traveling to new-york is between the person who's birthday is in july and the person who's birthday is in august##2
12. the craftsman house is on the left of the art-deco house##1
13. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the right of the french##5
14. the art-deco house is not the person traveling to berlin##6
15. the ranch-style house is the owner of the rabbit##1
16. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere between the turkish and the person traveling to boston##7
