.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-8-19::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, manager, writer, engineer
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, skydiving, filmmaking, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, handball, surfing, volleyball
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: montecristo, vegafina, chaman, alhambra
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, march, april, july
 1. the alhambra-smoker is the person who's sport is handball##1
 2. the engineer is on the far left##1
 3. the chaman-smoker is not to the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
 4. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 5. the alhambra-smoker is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
 6. the alhambra-smoker is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's birthday is in june##2
 7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not the lawyer##6
 8. the person who's birthday is in june is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
 9. the writer is not to the left of the alhambra-smoker##8
10. the lawyer is not to the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##8
11. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is not the person who's birthday is in march##6
12. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
13. the chaman-smoker is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
14. the chaman-smoker is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
15. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the left of the vegafina-smoker##8
16. the person who's birthday is in june is not to the right of the alhambra-smoker##8
17. the montecristo-smoker is not to the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##8
18. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in april##5
19. the person who's sport is lacrosse is the chaman-smoker##1
20. the person who's birthday is in july is the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3    |   4    |
| Job          | engineer | manager   | writer | lawyer   |
| Hobby   | skydiving     | filmmaking  | woodworking | collecting |
| Sport   | lacrosse  | surfing     | handball   | volleyball |
| Cigar           | chaman | vegafina     | alhambra  | montecristo   |
| Birthday     | july  | june | april    | march   |

