The people have 4 different jobs:  accountant, doctor, pilot, videographer
City: new-york, paris, berlin, london
 1. the person driving the train is somewhere to the left of the person who growsiris##5
 2. the person traveling to berlin is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to paris##5
 3. the person traveling to london is between the american and the person who growsamaryllis##2
 4. the person who growsiris is the pakistani##1
 5. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left##1
 6. the russian is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
 7. the doctor is on the left of the person who growsiris##1
 8. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the german##5
 9. the accountant is somewhere to the left of the videographer##5
10. the person driving the train is in an even position##4
11. the german is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
12. the pilot is not to the left of the russian##8
13. the pilot is the pakistani##1
14. the person driving the train is not to the right of the person who growszinnia##8
15. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
16. the person traveling to london is somewhere to the right of the russian##5

.:: Answer ::.
